//Player Endpoints
### Get All Players
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players

### Get Player by ID (admin - ID 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1

### Get Player by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/99999

### Get Player by ID (invalid ID - string)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid

### Create New Player
POST http://localhost:3000/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testplayer",
    "coins": 500,
    "lootboxCount": 5
}

### Create Player (duplicate username - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "coins": 1000
}

### Create Player (no username - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "coins": 1000
}

### Update Player Coins
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/coins
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "coins": 500000
}

### Update Player Lootbox Count
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/lootboxes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "lootboxCount": 50
}

### Update Player (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/players/99999/coins
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "coins": 100
}

